<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Завдання 2 - Випадаюче меню</title>
    <style>
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        
        
        
        .nav-menu {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex; 
            background-color: #5ba078; 
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            width: fit-content;
        }

        /* Пункти меню */
        .nav-menu li {
            position: relative; 
        }

        
        .nav-menu a {
            display: block;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        
        .nav-menu li:hover > a {
            background-color: #3e6d52;
        }

        
        .submenu, .inner-submenu {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #5ba078;
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 160px;
            z-index: 99; 
        }

        
        .nav-menu li:hover > .submenu {
            display: block;
        }

       
        .inner-submenu {
            top: 0;
            left: 100%; 
        }

        
        .has-children:hover > .inner-submenu {
            display: block;
        }

        .content-box {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h2 { margin-top: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <ul class="nav-menu">
            <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
            
            <li>
                <a href="#">Categories</a>
                <ul class="submenu">
                    <li><a href="#">Man</a></li>
                    
                    <li class="has-children">
                        <a href="#">Woomen</a>
                        <ul class="inner-submenu">
                            <li><a href="#">Dress</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Pants</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Shoes</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    
                    <li><a href="#">Kids</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Contacts</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="content-box">
        <h2>What is Lorem Ipsum?</h2>
        <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla ac augue quis ante blandit blandit eu et massa. 
            Integer libero dui, pellentesque id laoreet eu, dignissim non ex. Donec a purus non augue rutrum semper et quis justo. 
            Etiam ultrices ante at elit porttitor malesuada. Morbi feugiat tempus massa non venenatis. 
            Suspendisse id leo eros. Fusce sodales elementum purus, eu rutrum arcu blandit eu.
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>